<div class="jumbotron text-center">
    <h1>Coming Soon!</h1>
    <!-- Add Logo with Ruby Link -->
    <h3>Under Construction</h3>
    <h5>Small Team - Big Results</h5>
    <h6>Progress</h6>
    <div class="progress">
        <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="2" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 2%;"></div>
    </div>
</div>
<% if user_signed_in? %>
<div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
        <h3 class="panel-title text-center">Dashboard</h3>
    </div>
<div class="panel-body">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6">
            <div class="thumbnail">
                <div class="caption text-center">
                    <h2>Your Profile</h2>
                    <% if current_user.profile %>
                    <%= link_to "Edit your profile", "#", class: 'btn btn-default btn-lg btn-block' %>
          <%= link_to "View your profile", user_path(current_user), class: 'btn btn-default btn-lg btn-block' %>
        <% else %>
          <p>Create your profile so that you can share your information with the community.</p>
          <%= link_to "Create your profile", new_user_profile_path(current_user), class: 'btn btn-default btn-lg btn-block'%>
        <% end %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6">
                <div class="thumbnail">
                    <div class="caption text-center">
                        <h2>The Community</h2>
                        <p>Visit the community to meet other members with similar interests!</p>
        <%= link_to "Visit the community", "#", class: 'btn btn-default btn-lg btn-block' %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
    </div>
</div>
</div>
<% else %>
<div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
        <h3 class="panel-title text-center">Features</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
                <div class="thumbnail">
                    <div class="caption text-center">
                        <h3>Realistic Simulations</h3>
                        <p>We want to provide the best possible sports simulation! Games that are as close to the real thing as possible and still be a text based web game. Are you ready for Ultimate Sim Sports?</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
                <div class="thumbnail">
                    <div class="caption text-center">
                        <h3>Multiple Sports</h3>
                        <div class="col-xs-2 col-xs-offset-1 col-md-2 col-md-offset-1"><span class="icon ion-ios-basketball"></span></div>
                        <div class="col-xs-2 col-xs-offset-1 col-md-2 col-md-offset-1"><span class="icon ion-ios-americanfootball"></span></div>
                        <div class="col-xs-2 col-xs-offset-1 col-md-2 col-md-offset-1"><span class="icon ion-ios-baseball"></span></div>
                        <div class="col-xs-2 col-xs-offset-1 col-md-2 col-md-offset-1"><span class="icon ion-ios-football"></span></div>
                        <p>Our goal is to provide as many professional and college sports games as possible. We will begin with one sport and as interest increases we will increase the sports that are available. This is more than just fantasy sports this is Dynasty!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
                <div class="thumbnail">
                    <div class="caption text-center">
                        <h3>Dynasties</h3>
                        <p>Want to build your perfect dynasty? That is our specialty. Our goal is to provide one of the best Dynasty experiences on the internet. be the coach of your favorite team, take them to the top or to the bottom against other players and the AI. The choice is yours...</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
        <h3 class="panel-title text-center">Memberships</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6">
                <div class="thumbnail">
                    <div class="caption text-center">
                        <h3>Basic Account</h3>
                        <h6>Sign up for free and get basic access to the community.</h6>
                        <br/>
                        <%= link_to "Sign up Basic", new_user_registration_path(plan: @basic_plan.id), class: 'btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block' %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6">
                <div class="thumbnail">
                    <div class="caption text-center">
                        <h3>Pro Account</h3>
                        <h6>Sign up for the pro account for $10/month and get access to the community and web game!</h6>
                        <%= link_to "Sign up Pro", new_user_registration_path(plan: @pro_plan.id), class: 'btn btn-success btn-lg btn-block' %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <% end %>
</div>